  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Impulsive, always active and impatient, Falcons live life at high speed. They hate waiting, whether for the comfort of others or imperative circumstances, and they always look for ways to streamline and hurry things along. They are competitive in the most carefree way and love to compete for ephemeral laurels that give them great satisfaction, before moving on to the next challenge. They live in the present, and tend to be bad strategists but excellent executors, although prudence is never their strength. In the military, they are sought-after and highly regarded as reconnaissance and raiders, often employed in quick guerrilla tactics. Unfortunately, their incredible agility and dexterity, especially in flight, sometimes gives them the illusion of being invulnerable. In their relationships, Falcons tend to be changeable and reluctant to make enduring bonds, which they perceive as too limiting, and anyone who wants to entertain any type of relationship with them must be aware of this trend. They love to travel, to experience new and exciting things, and they fear boredom and monotony more than anything else.</span> <br style=\"font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:normal;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-size-adjust:auto\" /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Increase in Ability Scores.</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Your <span class=\"fontstyle0\">Charisma </span>score increases by 1 and your <span class=\"fontstyle0\">Dexterity </span>score increases by 2.<br /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Age.</strong></em> </span>A Rapax reaches maturity around the age of 14 <span class=\"fontstyle0\">and is immediately considered independent. They have an average lifespan of around 60 years.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Speed.  </strong></em></span></span>Your base speed on the ground is 15 feet, and your <span class=\"fontstyle0\">flight speed is 40 feet.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Size. </strong></em></span>A Falcon can reach a maximum height of 4 feet and <span class=\"fontstyle0\">a weight of no more than 65 lbs. Your size is Small.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Wild spirit.</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">You have proficiency in the Survival skill.</span></p>\n<p><em><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Feared. </span></strong></em><span class=\"fontstyle2\">You have proficiency in the Intimidate ability.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.ZLta2Wjm3OsgNAk0]{Wings}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.9ALHHLuQoSWQRqN4]{Prehensile Legs}</span></p>\n<p>@Compendium[world.species-features.2zVRhhfSO8fMZWzt]{Acute Sight}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[world.species-features.XXAgaQu5o3hNCwQA]{Rapax Claws}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[world.species-features.QuIdJAIbTc1h2oiV]{Rapax Peck}</p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.44XRzRoTdladuFme]{Elusive Attack}</span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.K3vkJOhbY84KuNmD]{Maneuvers in Flight}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><em><strong>Instinct of Familia, Distance (Predator):</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle4\">“I can analyze situations while keeping at a distance”.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle4\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Instinct of Species, Diving:</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">“I throw myself into action, danger cannot touch me.”</span> <br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /></span></p>",
      "chat": "",
